{% block description %}
     <p>
          Studio Connect is a platform connecting two communities who've been dying to meet each other:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>product designers at Target, looking for fast feedback &amp;</li>
          <li>their customers, looking for better products.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          The web & mobile executions made interesting use of React & React Native by sharing the API layer, reducing effort for updates.
        </p>
        <p>
          The mobile applications made use of Code Push, allowing updates to be sent & applied automatically, bypassing app store approvals
        </p>
        <p>Discussed in <a href='#'>Fast Company</a>, <a href='#'>Business Insider</a> & <a href='#'>Bustle</a>.</p>
